Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.31,0:00:06.06,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please can you keep my secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:23.54,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror, shining so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:29.38,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how do I look in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.80,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The future, beckoning me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:38.68,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen from now, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:49.94,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because what we see is not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.78,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing myself but that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:55.36,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now try not to waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:00.32,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be true to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:03.08,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But even I have a secret or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:10.63,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,That I want to keep to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.38,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my secret makes my heart aches slightly.
