Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Why did you tell everyone that you didn't want them to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so depressed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually wanted them to see you off, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning arrives, and school's over in a blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's as scary as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that devil Prez? That's because he was having lunch in class before break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even scolded him before the teacher could do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintani, why are you having lunch now?!  And it's only first period!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, aren't you afraid of getting scolded by her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, 'cause she's Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the sports clubs make this mess?  I told them many times not to track mud inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's communicating with the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, cleaning this up sure is back-breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! She'll bring you to hell if you get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose the Prez out of all the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,688)}She might have been kinder back then, but look at her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,688)}Are there any bad boys lurking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does talk a little differently compared to back then, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still as kind as she was!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confiscating these bread crusts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Don't tell me she treats me differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a masochist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she is still Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings for her won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized a long time ago that she has to be the one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get your new uniform dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? Pouting like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's middle school going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can make a lot of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time really flies! You're already in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm glad he grew up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worried about him everyday after he came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was plump back then, but he slimmed down a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause you only gave me veggies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being ridiculous!  You were the one who didn't want the meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it's fine, though you didn't look fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad things turned out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Come back to home base! {Ok, baseball term here, not sure how to phrase it, but literal TL is 'run around the bases'}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got faster, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't look all that muscular, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have them, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata's surprisingly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the ace, so of course he'd be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! He's such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I... actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Valentine's Day, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, okay?  You-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,UxMishi's live performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They're gonna perform in Yumesaki High's Cultural Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten how awful he was to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! Please tell her she can't go, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He supposedly got injured in his last performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and changed his attitude when she visited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!  But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has really changed, and I wanted you two to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I have to go, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go Yumesaki High's Cultural Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring him along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, you're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, masters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri Kari... Eri Kalipso!{consider dropping this phrase altogether, I find it retarded to just put down the line as heard}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Lady Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, will I!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, will I!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be together with Misa-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Let the crystal ball reveal your future with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a fitting fortune-teller, but she still lacks some {\i1}moe{\i0} points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at her. She's moves as if she's possessed by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so anxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been revealed! This is-!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything, since it's as cloudy as gray matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything! That's everything you need to know! In other words-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it'll never happen for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the crystal ball says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to put it so bluntly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since fortune-telling is basically just observing people, Misa wouldn't be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know about your own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan- Oops, it's Misa-chan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't come enough to remember to call you that. How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're already a regular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I saw outside that there's fortune-telling today. Can I get one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sit in front of the crystall ball, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how authentic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me my future with Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A paper balloon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is deflated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His future with Misa-chan's like a deflated paper balloon, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be worse than our cloudy prediction!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The deflated balloon's inflating again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to hang on to your last thread, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any holes in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved. I can just inflate it again as long as there are no holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite optimistic of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's something extra for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That optimism might just turn things around for you in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I'll get my future with Misa-chan told as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me, or am I seeing dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall look into your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{more trash}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{jibberish. Oh well, they're play-acting, so actually it mind have some meaning, "Erika mo miru!" > I'm seeing something!, but given the situation, it sounds like they're trying to put some crap in anyway, so I'd drop it}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally averting her eyes from the crystal ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's my fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah, r-right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell it to me straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have no future together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see fire and water in the crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are very incompatible, and a romance between the two of you cannot happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still wish to pursue this relationship, you will have to face a great obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to our fortunes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to tell us more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Erika, please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our turn yet, eh? Let's retreat quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Mr. Third Rate hurrying off somewhere just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really bother you that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be waiting for his situation to turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Third Rate were to hit the comeback homerun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So we were that incompatible with each other eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You aren't that easily influenced by fortune-telling, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the reason why you're so cold towards only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's 'cause you're a perverted alien-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're calling me that 'cause of our incompatibility, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not allowed to be together, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you going to leave me just because of this? {STRIKE OUT!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those guys from the sports clubs! I'll make them pay this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you going to leave me just because of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you, Misaki-chan! {aww hinata... you're fighting a losing battle}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your cleaning properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing, you've just completely changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You're a great help, Shintani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-r-really? I-I'm glad! I-I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintani, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!  I'll change the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so cute that I thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't it be faster to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the hose?  It might be long enough to get the whole entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Press here, just like this, and it'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Did you connect the hose properly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! Don't block the water with your hands! Turn off the tap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I turn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off! Don't use your hands to block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing on this chilly day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui, you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna catch a cold if you don't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop you if you insist on playing in the water, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.  Shintani, do you have clothes to change into?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my jersey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change quickly and head back. You're gonna catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What 'bout you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the infirmary and take care of this. See you later. Get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going there like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the corridors would get wet, so I'll walk around the building to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, right? Not like you can see through my underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Why do you think that guy over there is blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you feeling embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to be so clueless, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine! No big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strip completely if you don't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you're fine with me dancing stark naked at the school gates... {I'm sure many kwms fangirls will die imagining this e: I might die from imagining it, but for a different reason.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright already. Just don't go stripping, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruff! {barking sound. No really, barking sound e: LOL WARF?! WTF DID I JUST HEAR.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, just felt like doing it.  Why don't you try meowing? {If meow can be used as a verb that is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What are you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruff! {Awwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwww Hinataaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa T____T e: His tears are delicious & painful at the same time}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she might have one already, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially if she's as cute as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no worries if she's a fugly pig, though. {e: LOL DID YOU REALLY JUST USE FUGLY?! Fuck yes, I'm leaving that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not! She's definitely cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she must have a boyfriend by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You honestly never thought about that possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive! We're gonna be high schoolers soon, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the city girls, even for the middle schoolers, they must've...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a high school girl, I'm sure they have to have done {\i1}this{\i0} or {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try reading this book I found in my big sister's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The high school girls were playing around with a guy's body, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki wouldn't do things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a pure, cute, and kind person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't tease an idealistic middle school boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, don't you think that he needs to start seeing things more realistically?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he does worry others sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still has the candy wrapper that girl gave him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, you know?  He put that wrapper into the victory charm we bought together for the baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(579,671)}WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the reason we lost our second round in the summer league?! {league? baseball term here again}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! It was the reason why we won our first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{drop}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really serious about finding her in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be disappointed if you expect too much from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared if you're gonna try to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was prepared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll worry about getting her annoyed when it happens, and just keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days later... What a nice weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you waiting a long time for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Yumesaki High's Cultural Festival is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing! I was just about to film the lakeside scene that we didn't get to do last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are free, right?  Here, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all in the same boat, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks have been going off non-stop, so we'll cover up the audio later. I'll leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This year's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard rumors, but to think that it's this grand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it's their school's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they've spent half a year preparing for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really noisy over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've shown up eh? UxMishi, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura- She's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuga! Here's something for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I said it before? Be nice if you want me to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who can promise me that can follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura! Shizuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So both of you were swept up to the first few rows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond this sea of people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they were lining up for the performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Sakura doesn't want to move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna move! I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go further away from the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here!{Shizuko line}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we won't be able to meet up with you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so go ahead and enjoy yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh? Shizuko-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but... {Ok, editing required, leaving this like this is kinda... broken}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuga's changed recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The band has a different feel about them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem so tense. It feels like there's a gap between them and their fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But scandals involving the fans have faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good thing for their fans who are looking forward to their music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuga certainly seemed different, like Sakura said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm still not sure if he's trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:22:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about her...  So worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess a person's opinions differ when seen from different angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use thinking about it now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go and enjoy the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Enjoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel like I'm being led around by Usui...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, shall we enjoy ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly like that! {Referring to the way he speaks in previous line} You always talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:24:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy Yumesaki's Festival, since we're already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}Now you're switching to the spoilt brat tone! {Oh well, can't think of a phrase for it, you know, the kind of tone for a kiddo to get things that he wants}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}You're annoying, so go be with Shizuko and Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}When is KameMushi's live performance ending?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}It's UxMishi! I hope Kuuga will sing his new song!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}Oh yeah, shouldn't you tell everyone that next episode's the last one? {YOU BETTER FUCKING BE NIGGA}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,588)}I-Is it? Then I should do something befitting of the last episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.06,0:24:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,688)}I wanna see your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.23,0:24:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,688)}Usui, you idiot!
